Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.77,Flashback,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Orc Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.66,Flashback,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put an end to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:25.09,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1614,389)}That {\c&H471E13&}Time {\c&HCD9612&}I Got {\c&H471E13&}Reincarnated {\c&HCD9612&}as a {\c&H7E4F0A&}Slime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:42.42,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1357,1)}Episode 14: The One Who Devours All
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a majin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.53,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:16.70,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you ruin the great \NLord Gelmud's plans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Gelmud?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.62,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Gelmud is—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.48,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The one who named Rigurd's eldest son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.25,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:31.01,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,A new Demon Lord who would have done \Nmy bidding was about to be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:32.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,A new...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.24,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,...Demon Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.26,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:39.31,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I gave out so many \Nnames, sowed so many seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.77,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,All to create the ultimate pawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.15,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.98,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,...you showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.69,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,...in our village?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.16,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's Lord Gelmud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.40,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one who gave Sir Gabiru his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.66,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.05,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you've come to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.97,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,You useless dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:03.79,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.96,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Just become a meal for the Orc Lord already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.30,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.80,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:15.90,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,A useless fool like you will \Nnever be more than a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.56,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,So be eaten by the Orc Lord \Nand become his strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:24.31,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be useful to me in death. \NConsider it an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.82,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gero... G-Gel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.30,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, Orc Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.01,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.91,Main,Orc Lord,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by evolving \Ninto a Demon Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.48,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk... You really are an imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.42,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,You will become the Demon Lord "Orc Disaster"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.51,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,and rule over the entire Forest of Jura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.01,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,That is what both he and I desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.06,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.45,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing \Nthere, you dumb pig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:08.15,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time. I'm not supposed \Nto interfere, but I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.14,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Gabiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.44,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,You must flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.86,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.57,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:25.46,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Gabiru, you're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.54,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.02,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Gelmud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:48.52,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Become nourishment for the Orc Lord, \Nand be useful to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:54.65,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you the strength \Nof a superior majin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.45,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.62,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Deathmarch Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.89,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Gelmud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.34,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.98,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How's a move like that going to kill anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.27,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.07,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,You... You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.78,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They're healing potions. \NUse them on your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.70,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.93,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.95,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,You went through all this for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.04,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.42,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy is the one behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.28,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Gabiru was \Nfooled by someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.43,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But I've grown to like Gabiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.91,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the reason I need to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.98,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you do this to a superior maji—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.82,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying you're some bigshot \N"superior majin," but you're nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.58,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get it! \NYou can be on my side! I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:36.46,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You're finished! \NHe's going to make you regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:41.29,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me just who "he" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me who's pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.91,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.35,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Orc Lord! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.35,Main,Orc Lord,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.76,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I said help me, Orc Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.69,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... Geld!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.98,Flashback,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Geld.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.02,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Geld...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:10.38,Flashback,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you will take possession \Nof the Great Forest of Jura
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.22,Flashback,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,and become the Orc Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.96,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd hurry up and evolve \Ninto a Demon Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.67,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Finally moving now, you scumbag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.47,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to experience this beast's strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:38.48,Main,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Geld! Make them rue \Nthe day they defied m—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.55,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Gelmud's life signs have ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.12,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.99,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,He's eating him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.94,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.52,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,The Orc Lord Geld's magicules \Nhave vastly increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.02,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Evolution to Demon Lord is beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.73,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:35.67,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Geld has evolved into the Orc Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:40.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Orc Disaster, Geld, the Demon Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.36,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit and do nothing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:51.02,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Orc Disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.77,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who will \Ndevour all in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.02,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Geld...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.76,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Geld the Demon Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:06.82,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't kill him now, \Nit really will be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.36,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.03,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Right! On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.83,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let us handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:18.67,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a Demon Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.34,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Curb your ego, you foul pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:39.90,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,He got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's some insane healing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.56,sign_14664_116_Arcane_Thread_Fe,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(271,1)}Arcane Thread Fetters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.56,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Arcane Thread Fetters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.19,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Benimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.36,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Have some of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.86,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Out of magicules?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.26,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.07,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang out in my shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:43.50,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:52.12,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.99,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,So this... is pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.95,Main,General,0000,0000,0000,,My king, I offer my body to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.22,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Self-regeneration and healing magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.74,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough! I need more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.85,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.01,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.59,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I have a trick up my sleeve, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.96,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit cowardly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.64,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're up, Great Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.34,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you! Defeat my enemy at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:16.80,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Switching to auto-battle mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.64,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what Great Sage can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:29.61,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Devour all! Chaos Eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:47.05,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, nice! I knew I could \Ncount on Great Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.01,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:06.48,Main,General,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:19.24,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I will eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.61,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to devour you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.39,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Flare Circle! This'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.05,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Operation complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.40,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Great Sage! That went perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.40,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.97,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency has arisen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.64,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... He has fire resistance now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.37,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.02,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately recalculating—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.17,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over, Great Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.93,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.18,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've figured out how \Nto defeat him, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:23.35,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So just leave the rest to me, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.90,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,It appears fire has no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:37.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? You might have \Nbeen happier burning to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I've acknowledged you as an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:44.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll take you on for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.08,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Laughable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.97,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you weren't \Nserious before now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.21,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing more you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.44,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept that I'm going to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Before you can eat me, I'm going to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.39,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.29,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.73,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.61,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who can eat things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.74,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Will you eat me first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,or will I eat you first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.43,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The one who completely \Nconsumes the other wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.39,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Between your Starved
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.98,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and my Predator...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.71,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Which is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:03.93,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will be my Predator...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.79,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, if you are "Starved," then I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.98,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,a "Devourer"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.99,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry? Wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.75,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.48,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Eat well, and grow up big and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.83,Flashback,Orc,0000,0000,0000,,My king, please don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:54.40,Flashback,Orc,0000,0000,0000,,In this great famine, \Nif we were to lose even you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.88,Flashback,Orc,0000,0000,0000,,nothing would await us but despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:02.10,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,The child born only two \Ndays ago died this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.29,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,The child born yesterday is at death's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:09.51,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,My body will always regenerate \Nany parts I tear off, but this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:15.84,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,If this is not a state of despair \Nalready, what else is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.82,Flashback,Orc,0000,0000,0000,,My king...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.26,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I will go into the forest to search for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.83,Flashback,Orc,0000,0000,0000,,But the Forest of Jura has the divine \Nprotection of the Storm Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:32.00,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,The Storm Dragon has long been sealed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.35,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I must seek even the slightest blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.51,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so hungry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.55,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to eat something... anything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.10,Flashback,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you a name and some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.35,Flashback,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.85,Flashback,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Gelmud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.60,Flashback,Gelmud,0000,0000,0000,,Think of me as your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:10.16,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that anyone I ate as the Orc Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:13.62,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,would not die, being under \Nthe control of Starved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:17.70,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he was merely using \Nme as a pawn in his evil scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.57,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,but I had to take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.28,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I must eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.22,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a slime \Nthat can eat anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.18,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let myself be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to eating, I have \Nthe advantage. You'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.99,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I ate all the monsters I encountered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:40.65,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I ate Lord Gelmud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.31,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I even ate my brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.90,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,My brethren are starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.24,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,So I cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, it's eat or be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:59.99,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost, so you're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:03.42,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:07.42,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, my sins fall upon \Nmy brethren's shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.68,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,It matters not if I am sinful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.68,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure that they don't starve,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.68,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I must take all the world's \Nhunger upon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:26.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But rest easy. I'll devour all \Nyour sins along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.19,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Devour... my sins?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour the sins of all your brethren, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.37,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Even the sins of my brethren?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.38,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,You are greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I am greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.64,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Greedy one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.37,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,One who devours my sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.00,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.71,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,My hunger has now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.55,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,been sated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.33,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.64,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,The Orc Disaster is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace, Geld.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:57.62,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,With the Orc Lord defeated, \Nthe effects of Starved also vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:02.02,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, the advance \Nof the Orcs was halted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.48,Main,General,0000,0000,0000,,My king...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:15.17,Main,General,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally been set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.39,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.39,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:27.99,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I promised that you'd be free \Nonce the Orc Lord was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.49,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.36,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.54,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept our allegiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:43.24,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,We will continue to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:45.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.25,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,I have no objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:52.09,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,We are truly fortunate to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.66,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your secretary and \Nbodyguard, Rimuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.72,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never leave your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.66,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not until the ends of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.64,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.11,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Jura Forest Alliance."
